{"tid":779413,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"墮駒仇思達衝出嚟柒，今日陳浩天講修改基本法","createTime":"2018-08-14T11:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T05:11:01.000Z","uid":43785,"like":10,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"102bba383298810c03b61d60378503072f1c04c0","tid":779413,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:24:52.000Z","msg":"墮駒仇思達今次真係衝出嚟柒，<br />\n連陳浩天講乜野都唔知就出文駁人，<br />\n今日陳浩天搬龍門講修改基本法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/14/Bp3nsj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2FBp3nsj.png&h=987b1803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/14/wIT4rY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2FwIT4rY.png&h=c04d9f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當初又話修改基本法唔可行，要廢憲建國，點解今日陳浩天講修改基本法，班本民青都要打晒飛機。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我唔撚鍾意個殘獸惠，不過今次講得好，搞到墮駒中伏，值得貼堂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9472f9b5332e08959a65f1b782b5615d853f4c6","tid":779413,"uid":43785,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:26:28.000Z","msg":"仇狗每次都衝出黎柒🐕🐩🐅🐆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c01caef47b294498f1af3011dc0353d3780cb1","tid":779413,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/uploa